      "html": "<p block-type=\"ListGroup\"><ul><li block-type=\"ListItem\"> by running company exposure data through commercially available cat modeling software, or</li><li block-type=\"ListItem\"> by designing payout functions along some parametric indicators (e.g., the Richter scale of an earthquake at a specified location, an aggregate industry loss index, etc.).</li></ul></p>",
