      "id": "/page/0/TextInlineMath/14",
      "block_type": "TextInlineMath",
      "html": "<p block-type=\"TextInlineMath\">Lane showed that his model (1) fits reasonably well to empirical prices for a dozen CAT bond transactions in 1999–2000, for which the best-fit parameters were <math display=\"inline\">\\gamma = 55\\%</math>, <math display=\"inline\">\\alpha = 49\\%</math>, and <math display=\"inline\">\\beta = 57\\%</math>.</p>",
