    {
      "id": "/page/0/Text/16",
      "block_type": "Text",
      "html": "<p block-type=\"Text\">Wang [2] establishes a pricing method by directly applying the following Wang transform to convert a loss curve <i>S</i> to a price curve <math display=\"inline\">S^*</math>:</p>",
      "page": 225,
