    {
      "id": "/page/0/Text/18",
      "block_type": "Text",
      "html": "<p block-type=\"Text\">where <math display=\"inline\">t</math> represents Student-<math display=\"inline\">t</math> distribution with degree of freedom <math display=\"inline\">k</math>. The difference in the areas between <math display=\"inline\">S^*</math> and S constitutes the risk load. Based on the same 1999–2000 cat bond transaction data as in [1], the estimated parameters of Wang transform in</p>",
